Text: Dimensional Fund Advisors LP lifted its position in CNB Financial by 5.3% during the 4th quarter. Dimensional Fund Advisors LP now owns 560,546 shares of the bank's stock valued at $12,864,000 after acquiring an additional 28,236 shares during the period.
